Demonstration of MPMD.

As before, we can see the evidence of "multiple data" as each process has a
copy of `rank` and `size`.

The "multiple program" part comes from the fact that The `prog_rank_1` program
(not the rank-1 process), is a different program than `prog_rank_2`. This is
due to the `if`-statment that checks for rank of the processes.
